        <abstract> 
<p>CD and his brother Erasmus have read EK’s article on Erasmus Darwin. Asks whether EK would object to a translation by W. Dallas, to be offered to <hi rend="italic">Fortnightly Review</hi> or to be published at CD’s expense as a book.</p> 
